In [[cryptography]], '''CJCSG''' is a [[stream cipher|stream cypher]] [[algorithm]] developed by [[Cees Jansen]] and [[Alexander Kolosha]]. It has been submitted to the [[eSTREAM]] Project of the [[eCRYPT]] network. It has been classified as an archival algorithm and will not be further considered. 

